{"tid":840152,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"個人覺得今屆利記係好有機會拿冠軍的一年","createTime":"2018-09-28T12:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T13:25:54.000Z","uid":125470,"like":14,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a15aa4569e0e107977795e4aa84d8c6ace6fcc54","tid":840152,"uid":125470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:56:37.000Z","msg":"個人覺得今屆係好有機會拿冠軍的一年<br />\n比去年更大機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡單分析幾個主要對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曼聯 &mdash; 普巴同主帥摩連奴既關係處於前所未有既低點 隊內軍心不穩其實佢地實力削弱左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先講後防 除了中堅拜利係具有級數，其餘都不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 史摩寧及菲爾鐘斯無論是默契表現、後防補位、轉身速度、還是判斷、 防守意識等，都令人懷疑佢地是否有效力豪門球會既能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中前場全能到仆街既山齊士「山神」已經無以前咁大殺傷力~我唔信馬達同華舒福可以組織起有效率既進攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 單單依賴一個盧卡古係唔足夠~個人認為靴里拉同連格特幫助不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n車仔 &mdash; 今屆開始佢地係開得好好~但唔好忘記佢D對手係好平凡<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只有一仗對阿（妓）叫做強D~另外就係佢D主將開始老了<br />\n無記錯柏度~韋利安～基奧特~大衛雷斯~法比加斯~等等都過了三十了<br />\n可不可以頂住緊密賽程係一個大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同個人覺得沙利唔係一個咁有料的人~有幾多個好似高普咁有感染力<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴 &mdash; 雲加走左根本無佈陣可言~個人覺得佢地穩定性比利記仲差<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n曼城 &mdash; 雖然佢地錢多人多~但係重中之重奇雲迪布尼傷左始終有一定影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋B沙維都係一般般~暫時沒有冠軍相<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於利物浦今年雖然走了古天奴 但一支球隊唔會話走左一個人就會差成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人覺得納比基達攻擊力比古天奴更好~(不喜勿插)~有待時間証明<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今屆開季聯賽七戰全勝~氣勢之盛可謂一時無兩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輸一場半場盃賽球員自然唔會驕傲自滿而得意忘形<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無記錯~七場勝仗當中沙拿、費明奴仍然提升緊比賽狀態~今屆好明顯高普比過去更懂得養精蓄銳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望明晚可以殺低車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一鼓作氣過埋曼城呢關~保持氣勢到季尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位巴打一條心支持利記今屆奪首個英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6bf6b4dacceff45122f12b7699843cfbe1ce6c","tid":840152,"uid":87272,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"今年攞唔到就越黎越遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592cdd0edcf58cd20f21393bca75b17467952ff1","tid":840152,"uid":125470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a6bf6b4dacceff45122f12b7699843cfbe1ce6c","tid":840152,"uid":87272,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"今年攞唔到就越黎越遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T13:01:36.000Z","msg":"利物浦開始復興了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078626f56b3e1f7e517d25095dc1b455fc5ffdac","tid":840152,"uid":58163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b6cc21cfd1ed0fc36aab1b7b2841c369434543","tid":840152,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0a6bf6b4dacceff45122f12b7699843cfbe1ce6c","tid":840152,"uid":87272,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"今年攞唔到就越黎越遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T13:02:40.00